{"title": "Free Roof Inspection in Utah | Local Licensed Crew", "slug": "free-roof-inspection-utah", "status": "draft", "content": "<style>\n/* ===== Rooval free-inspection landing page - scoped to this page only ===== */\n/* Hide the entire theme header + footer. The header's middle row carries a\n   competing \"Get a Free Estimate\" CTA to a separate funnel plus a duplicate\n   logo, so we hide #header wholesale; .rv-callbar below supplies logo +\n   tap-to-call. Fails safe: if :has() is unsupported, the theme chrome simply\n   reappears and nothing breaks. */\nbody:has(#rooval-lp) #header,\nbody:has(#rooval-lp) footer[data-elementor-type=\"footer\"]{display:none!important;}\n\n#rooval-lp{--rv-navy:#12233b;--rv-blue:#1f6feb;--rv-blue-dark:#155ac1;--rv-ink:#1b2733;--rv-muted:#5b6b7b;--rv-line:#e2e8f0;--rv-bg-soft:#f4f7fb;--rv-star:#f5a623;box-sizing:border-box;color:var(--rv-ink);line-height:1.55;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;font-size:17px;}\n#rooval-lp *,#rooval-lp *::before,#rooval-lp *::after{box-sizing:border-box;}\n#rooval-lp img{max-width:100%;height:auto;}\n\n/* --- slim, subordinate tap-to-call bar (logo + phone) --- */\n#rooval-lp .rv-callbar{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:12px;padding:8px 16px;background:var(--rv-bg-soft);border-bottom:1px solid var(--rv-line);}\n#rooval-lp .rv-callbar-logo{display:flex;align-items:center;}\n#rooval-lp .rv-callbar-logo img{max-height:34px;width:auto;display:block;}\n#rooval-lp .rv-callbar-logo .rv-wordmark{font-weight:700;font-size:18px;color:var(--rv-navy);letter-spacing:.2px;}\n#rooval-lp .rv-callbar-phone{font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:var(--rv-navy);text-decoration:none;white-space:nowrap;}\n#rooval-lp .rv-callbar-phone:hover{text-decoration:underline;}\n\n/* --- hero --- */\n#rooval-lp .hero-section{padding:40px 16px 8px;text-align:center;}\n#rooval-lp h1.page-title{font-size:2rem;line-height:1.2;margin:0 auto 14px;max-width:640px;color:var(--rv-navy);font-weight:800;}\n#rooval-lp .rv-subhead{font-size:1.12rem;color:var(--rv-muted);max-width:620px;margin:0 auto 24px;}\n\n/* --- buttons --- */\n#rooval-lp .rv-btn{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;min-height:54px;padding:15px 34px;background:var(--rv-blue);color:#fff;font-size:1.12rem;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;border-radius:10px;border:0;cursor:pointer;box-shadow:0 4px 14px rgba(31,111,235,.28);transition:background .15s ease,transform .05s ease;text-align:center;}\n#rooval-lp .rv-btn:hover{background:var(--rv-blue-dark);color:#fff;}\n#rooval-lp .rv-btn:active{transform:translateY(1px);}\n#rooval-lp .rv-btn-fallback{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;min-height:48px;padding:12px 26px;background:#fff;color:var(--rv-blue);font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;border:2px solid var(--rv-blue);border-radius:10px;}\n#rooval-lp .rv-btn-fallback:hover{background:var(--rv-bg-soft);color:var(--rv-blue-dark);}\n\n/* --- reassurance + trust strips --- */\n#rooval-lp .rv-reassure{font-size:.95rem;color:var(--rv-muted);margin:14px auto 0;}\n#rooval-lp .rv-trust-strip{margin:22px auto 0;font-size:.98rem;color:var(--rv-navy);font-weight:600;max-width:620px;}\n#rooval-lp .rv-stars{color:var(--rv-star);letter-spacing:1px;}\n\n/* --- entry content sections --- */\n#rooval-lp .entry-content{max-width:720px;margin:0 auto;padding:8px 16px 48px;}\n#rooval-lp .rv-section{padding:34px 0;border-top:1px solid var(--rv-line);}\n#rooval-lp .rv-section:first-child{border-top:0;}\n#rooval-lp .entry-content h2{font-size:1.5rem;color:var(--rv-navy);margin:0 0 20px;text-align:center;font-weight:800;}\n#rooval-lp .entry-content p{margin:0 0 16px;}\n\n/* --- steps --- */\n#rooval-lp .rv-steps{list-style:none;margin:0;padding:0;display:grid;gap:16px;}\n#rooval-lp .rv-step{display:flex;gap:16px;align-items:flex-start;background:var(--rv-bg-soft);border:1px solid var(--rv-line);border-radius:12px;padding:18px 20px;}\n#rooval-lp .rv-step-num{flex:0 0 auto;width:38px;height:38px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--rv-blue);color:#fff;font-weight:800;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:1.05rem;}\n#rooval-lp .rv-step h3{margin:0 0 4px;font-size:1.1rem;color:var(--rv-navy);}\n#rooval-lp .rv-step p{margin:0;color:var(--rv-muted);font-size:.98rem;}\n\n/* --- figures (house style) --- */\n#rooval-lp figure{margin:28px auto;max-width:560px;}\n#rooval-lp figure img{width:100%;height:auto;border-radius:10px;}\n#rooval-lp figure figcaption{text-align:center;font-size:.9rem;color:var(--rv-muted);margin-top:8px;}\n\n/* --- credentials list --- */\n#rooval-lp .rv-creds{list-style:none;margin:0 auto;padding:0;max-width:520px;display:grid;gap:12px;}\n#rooval-lp .rv-creds li{display:flex;gap:10px;align-items:flex-start;font-size:1rem;}\n#rooval-lp .rv-creds .rv-check{color:var(--rv-blue);font-weight:800;flex:0 0 auto;}\n\n/* --- reassurance / guardrail callout --- */\n#rooval-lp .rv-callout{background:var(--rv-bg-soft);border-left:4px solid var(--rv-blue);border-radius:8px;padding:20px 22px;font-size:1.02rem;color:var(--rv-ink);}\n\n/* --- booking section --- */\n#rooval-lp #book{scroll-margin-top:16px;}\n#rooval-lp .rv-book-trust{text-align:center;font-size:.98rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--rv-navy);margin:0 0 18px;}\n#rooval-lp #book-frame-wrap{position:relative;min-height:760px;border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;background:var(--rv-bg-soft);border:1px solid var(--rv-line);}\n#rooval-lp .book-loading{position:absolute;inset:0;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;color:var(--rv-muted);font-size:1rem;z-index:0;padding:24px;text-align:center;}\n#rooval-lp #book-frame-wrap iframe{width:100%;min-height:760px;border:0;position:relative;z-index:1;display:block;background:transparent;}\n#rooval-lp .rv-fallback{text-align:center;margin-top:16px;font-size:.98rem;color:var(--rv-muted);}\n#rooval-lp .rv-fallback a{margin-top:8px;}\n\n/* --- bottom repeat CTA --- */\n#rooval-lp .rv-final{text-align:center;background:var(--rv-navy);border-radius:14px;padding:38px 24px;color:#fff;margin-top:8px;}\n#rooval-lp .rv-final h2{color:#fff;margin-bottom:10px;}\n#rooval-lp .rv-final .rv-reassure{color:#c8d6e8;}\n#rooval-lp .rv-final-call{display:block;margin-top:18px;color:#fff;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;font-size:1.05rem;}\n#rooval-lp .rv-final-call:hover{text-decoration:underline;}\n\n/* --- mobile-first responsive --- */\n@media (max-width:600px){\n  #rooval-lp{font-size:16px;}\n  #rooval-lp h1.page-title{font-size:1.6rem;}\n  #rooval-lp .rv-callbar{position:sticky;top:0;z-index:50;}\n  #rooval-lp .hero-section .rv-btn,\n  #rooval-lp .rv-final .rv-btn{display:flex;width:100%;}\n  #rooval-lp .rv-section{padding:28px 0;}\n}\n@media (min-width:601px){\n  #rooval-lp h1.page-title{font-size:2.4rem;}\n}\n</style>\n\n<div id=\"rooval-lp\">\n\n  <!-- Slim, subordinate logo + tap-to-call bar (sticky on mobile only) -->\n  <div class=\"rv-callbar\">\n    <span class=\"rv-callbar-logo\">\n      <img src=\"https://rooval-roofing.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/rooval-roofing-logo-optimized.webp\" alt=\"Rooval Roofing\" />\n    </span>\n    <a class=\"rv-callbar-phone\" href=\"tel:+13854248810\">Call (385) 424-8810</a>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- HERO -->\n  <div class=\"hero-section is-width-constrained\" data-type=\"type-1\">\n    <header class=\"entry-header\">\n      <h1 class=\"page-title\" itemprop=\"headline\">Get a free roof inspection from a local Utah crew</h1>\n    </header>\n    <p class=\"rv-subhead\">Storm or just wondering? We'll check your roof, photograph anything we find, and hand you a clear write-up. What you do next is up to you.</p>\n    <a class=\"rv-btn\" href=\"#book\">Book My Free Inspection</a>\n    <p class=\"rv-reassure\">Free look, no strings &mdash; you keep the write-up either way.</p>\n    <p class=\"rv-trust-strip\"><span class=\"rv-stars\">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</span> 5.0 stars &middot; Licensed Utah GC &middot; Local Lehi crew</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- ENTRY CONTENT: trust ladder -> booking -> repeat CTA -->\n  <div class=\"entry-content is-layout-constrained\">\n\n    <!-- 2. What happens -->\n    <section class=\"rv-section\">\n      <h2>What happens at your inspection</h2>\n      <ol class=\"rv-steps\">\n        <li class=\"rv-step\">\n          <span class=\"rv-step-num\">1</span>\n          <div><h3>We inspect</h3><p>A licensed Rooval roofer gets up there and checks the shingles, flashing, and vents for hail or wind damage.</p></div>\n        </li>\n        <li class=\"rv-step\">\n          <span class=\"rv-step-num\">2</span>\n          <div><h3>We document</h3><p>We photograph and note any storm damage, and give you a clear write-up of what we find.</p></div>\n        </li>\n        <li class=\"rv-step\">\n          <span class=\"rv-step-num\">3</span>\n          <div><h3>You decide</h3><p>You get a clear write-up so you can file with your insurer if you choose.</p></div>\n        </li>\n      </ol>\n    </section>\n\n    <!-- 3. Real-photo proof -->\n    <section class=\"rv-section\">\n      <h2>A recent inspection in Murray, Utah</h2>\n      <figure style=\"margin:28px auto;max-width:560px\">\n        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://rooval-roofing.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/utah-wasatch-front-asphalt-shingle-roof.jpg\" alt=\"Asphalt shingle roof on a Utah Wasatch Front home\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"width:100%;height:auto;border-radius:10px\" />\n      </figure>\n      <figure style=\"margin:28px auto;max-width:560px\">\n        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://rooval-roofing.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/roof-inspection-murray-utah.jpg\" alt=\"Rooval inspector marking damaged shingles during a roof inspection in Murray, Utah\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"width:100%;height:auto;border-radius:10px\" />\n        <figcaption>A real Rooval inspection in Murray, Utah.</figcaption>\n      </figure>\n    </section>\n\n    <!-- 4. Reviews / credentials -->\n    <section class=\"rv-section\">\n      <h2>A local crew you can check up on</h2>\n      <ul class=\"rv-creds\">\n        <li><span class=\"rv-check\">&#10003;</span> <span><strong>5.0 stars</strong></span></li>\n        <li><span class=\"rv-check\">&#10003;</span> <span>Licensed Utah general contractor &mdash; DOPL #13861046-5501</span></li>\n        <li><span class=\"rv-check\">&#10003;</span> <span>Local Lehi crew serving 16 Wasatch Front cities</span></li>\n        <li><span class=\"rv-check\">&#10003;</span> <span>Backed by our workmanship warranty</span></li>\n      </ul>\n    </section>\n\n    <!-- 5. Compliant reassurance -->\n    <section class=\"rv-section\">\n      <div class=\"rv-callout\">\n        We inspect your roof and document storm damage for your records, so you can file with your insurer. We're roofers, not insurance agents &mdash; you and your insurer handle the claim.\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <!-- 6. Booking (the iframe) -->\n    <section class=\"rv-section\" id=\"book\">\n      <h2>Pick a time that works for you</h2>\n      <p class=\"rv-book-trust\"><span class=\"rv-stars\">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</span> 5.0 stars &middot; Licensed Utah GC &middot; Free, no obligation</p>\n      <div id=\"book-frame-wrap\">\n        <div class=\"book-loading\" aria-hidden=\"true\">Loading your scheduler&hellip;</div>\n        <iframe src=\"https://rooval-crm-production.up.railway.app/quote\"\n          title=\"Book your free roof inspection\"\n          style=\"width:100%;min-height:760px;border:0;border-radius:12px;position:relative;z-index:1\"></iframe>\n      </div>\n      <p class=\"rv-fallback\">Form not loading?<br />\n        <a class=\"rv-btn-fallback\" href=\"https://rooval-crm-production.up.railway.app/quote\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Open the booking form</a>\n      </p>\n    </section>\n\n    <!-- 7. Repeat CTA + tap-to-call -->\n    <section class=\"rv-section\">\n      <div class=\"rv-final\">\n        <h2>Book your inspection</h2>\n        <a class=\"rv-btn\" href=\"#book\">Book My Free Inspection</a>\n        <a class=\"rv-final-call\" href=\"tel:+13854248810\">Or call (385) 424-8810</a>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n  </div><!-- /.entry-content -->\n</div><!-- /#rooval-lp -->\n", "meta_desc": "Book a free, no-obligation roof inspection with Rooval's local licensed Utah crew. We inspect, document any storm damage, and you decide what's next."}